    "Figure 33 shows the relative performance of the five deep learning algorithms and 1NN-DTW.",
    "Averaged statistics are shown in Table 12.",
    "The results confirm our prior belief: CNN is no better than 1NN-DTW, ResNet is significantly better than CNN, and InceptionTime is significantly better than ResNet.",
    "They also confirm recent findings in Ismail-Fawaz et al. (2022) and Ismail-Fawaz et al.",
    "(2023b): H-InceptionTime gives a small, but significant improvement over InceptionTime and LiteTime is as accurate as InceptionTime but takes a fraction of the time."
  ],
